msgid ""
"Kollision is a casual game where you need to throw your ball and avoid the "
"others balls on the table as long as possible."
msgstr ""
"Kollision je ležérna loptová hra, kde potrebujete hodiť loptu a vyhnúť sa "
"ostatným loptám na stole, kým je to možné."
